      "date": "2014-10-10 07:25:55.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/34082516-504d-11e4-8f8d-5254006e85c2).  Ran 15 tests.  1 tests failed: replay-ost-single.",
