          "date": "2014-10-08 13:37:20.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-5077 ptlrpc: simplify checsum calculation for reply",
        "message": "LU-5077 ptlrpc: simplify checsum calculation for reply\n\nIt's not necessary to call external crypto API to calculate chksum\nfor the small ptlrpc body on reply, instead, call crc32_le() directly\ncould avoid memory allocation.\n\nThis patch could fix the problem of OOM in crytpo_create_tfm(), or\nmake the OOM happen in other code path, then we can collect more\ninformation for further analysis.\n\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <yawei.niu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I604f24015d7f7c5293d43ad0dd34f852a75953f2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
